- He was that kind of player.

547
00:20:29,071 --> 00:20:30,840
A legendary player from the Major League joined our team.

548
00:20:30,841 --> 00:20:31,841
- Right.
- Yes.

549
00:20:31,842 --> 00:20:34,440
