564
00:21:04,511 --> 00:21:06,540
Shin Soo suggested this idea to the team first,

565
00:21:06,541 --> 00:21:08,480
- Right.
- and it changed a lot in KBO.

566
00:21:08,481 --> 00:21:09,780
Let me tell you what Shin Soo is to me.

567
