- People swear all the time.

623
00:23:10,101 --> 00:23:11,530
- That's what I noticed.
- He makes errors playing defense.

624
00:23:11,531 --> 00:23:13,600
Let's say I when to the stadium to watch the game.

625
00:23:13,601 --> 00:23:15,570
If there's a big score gap when I'm there to watch the game,

