644
00:23:53,011 --> 00:23:55,041
"Call me when this inning is over." Then she left.

645
00:23:56,711 --> 00:23:57,981
- That's what she did.
- "When the inning is over?"

646
00:23:58,681 --> 00:23:59,850
- "Call me when they switch."
- I need to be back...

647
00:23:59,851 --> 00:24:01,021
