655
00:24:17,371 --> 00:24:18,371
- Why?
- What?

656
00:24:18,372 --> 00:24:20,201
- That's what I heard.
- Right.

657
00:24:20,471 --> 00:24:21,900
Even though they are in the first place,

658
00:24:21,901 --> 00:24:23,340
- there are too many games.
- Right.

659
00:24:23,341 --> 00:24:25,040
The game will give you a headache at least two times a week.

660
00:24:25,041 --> 00:24:26,240
That's true.

661
00:24:26,241 --> 00:24:27,881
This is what I think.

662
00:24:28,281 --> 00:24:30,250
For the team that's in the first place.

663
00:24:30,251 --> 00:24:31,550
And for the team that's in last place.

664
00:24:31,551 --> 00:24:33,780
They'll win 60 games and lose 60 games.

665
00:24:33,781 --> 00:24:35,081
- Right.
- Yes.

666
00:24:35,151 --> 00:24:37,390
There are games that we lose no matter what.

667
00:24:37,391 --> 00:24:39,420
- Right.
- You'll know when you watch it.

668
00:24:39,421 --> 00:24:40,760
About baseball,

669
00:24:40,761 --> 00:24:43,160
