678
00:24:59,711 --> 00:25:01,540
About the baseball fans being angry all the time...

679
00:25:01,541 --> 00:25:03,310
This is my case. Personally, I get angry easily.

680
00:25:03,311 --> 00:25:04,750
Yes. We're well aware of it.

681
