683
00:25:09,921 --> 00:25:11,320
- You really are a huge fan.
- As I watch the game...

684
00:25:11,321 --> 00:25:13,890
Let's say the game starts at 6pm until 9pm.

685
00:25:13,891 --> 00:25:16,860
