688
00:25:19,161 --> 00:25:20,500
I eat as I watch the game.

689
00:25:20,501 --> 00:25:22,001
Gosh, Jang Hoon. That was a good point.

690
00:25:23,271 --> 00:25:25,200
- That was smart.
- She watches the game...

691
00:25:25,201 --> 00:25:26,770
