692
00:25:26,771 --> 00:25:28,370
Some people might think that you're solely focused on the game.

693
00:25:28,371 --> 00:25:30,141
- They might misunderstand.
- That's not the case.

694
00:25:30,241 --> 00:25:32,211
That's not true, but it was nice, Jang Hoon.

695
00:25:33,111 --> 00:25:34,680
- He's like Shin Soo today.
- Anyway,

696
00:25:34,681 --> 00:25:36,950
- I watch the game while eating.
- He jokes like Shin Soo.

697
00:25:36,951 --> 00:25:39,850
If the game doesn't go as I want... Of course, I even find walking hard,

698
00:25:39,851 --> 00:25:41,921
